Class ListReleasesMojo

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.maven.plugin.AbstractMojo
      • org.microbean.helm.maven.AbstractHelmMojo
        • org.microbean.helm.maven.AbstractReleaseMojo
          • org.microbean.helm.maven.ListReleasesMojo
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ContextEnabled, Mojo

    @Mojo(name="list")
public class ListReleasesMojo
extends AbstractReleaseMojo
    Retrieves releases matching certain criteria and notifies registered listeners.
    Author:
    Laird Nelson

        protected void execute(Callable<ReleaseManager> releaseManagerCallable)
                throws Exception
        Performs a release-oriented task using a ReleaseManager available from the supplied Callable.

        This implementation retrieves information about releases and notifies registered ReleaseDiscoveryListeners.
